        <div id="content">
          <section id="abstract">
            <h2>Abstract</h2>
            <div datatype="rdf:HTML" property="schema:abstract">
              <p>The purpose of this workshop is the mobilisation of a core group of researchers and practitioners to investigate the core characteristics of a minimal viable platform for scholarly communication that is decentralised, researcher-centric, interlinked, and web-native. As visible outcomes, this workshop aims to deliver initial insights regarding these core characteristics and will determine the most appropriate approach to engage in a sustained effort aimed at tackling technical challenges and promoting adoption of solutions.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

